Text.val: 15.11.2012 AS SCR#17691 fixed form output with expressions where attribute was ANSI instead of Unicode

ExpSyntax.val: MlsTrans ('Overview enterd schedules for confidential clients enterd by : ')&Trim ({0,1})

SQL_STMT_U.val: SELECT TCSC_ADMNO,TCSC_CLNTNO,CLNT110_NAME1, TCSC_SCHTNOCLI, TCSC_SCHEDDATE, TCSC_CURRENCY, TCCO_COUNTRY, TCCO_TOTADEBTNOTES, TCCO_TOTNDEBTNOTES, TCCO_TOTACREDNOTES, TCCO_TOTNCREDNOTES, TCSC_NO FROM :1/TCSC AS TCSC, :1/TCCO AS TCCO, :1/CLNT AS CLNT WHERE TCSC.TCSC_ADMNO=CLNT.CLNT101_ADMNO and TCSC.TCSC_CLNTNO= CLNT.CLNT102_CLNTNO and TCSC_NO=TCCO_TCSC_NO AND TCSC.TCSC_USRIDENTERED=':2' ORDER BY TCSC_RUNNUMBER , TCSC_CLNTNO, TCSC_SCHTNOCLI
